Put the spoon down in the right side of the sink, rinse off the spoon, pick up the spoon.
Turn left and walk back over to the black table.
Put the spoon down on the table in front of the paper towels.

high_descs: Turn around and walk to the table.
Pick up the spoon on the table.
Turn around and veer left to the sink.
Wash the spoon in the sink.
Turn left and walk back to the table, this time to the right side of it.
Place the spoon on the table on top of the spatula closest to you.

pick up the spoon off of the table

put the spoon inside the sink and fill it with water then drain the sink and remove the spoon
